{"tid":317456,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"E-kids 成員向考生分享讀書心得","createTime":"2017-07-11T12:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T11:06:01.000Z","uid":38407,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4385e16008f003c3a09f9a2c6c547b4b9fdfa268","tid":317456,"uid":38407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:42:35.000Z","msg":"E-Kids：會考每晚捱通宵 <br />\n<br />\nE-Kids 成員 Tommy 當年很害怕中五會考，笑說自己讀書成績一向不好 ，學校老師也經常提醒他們會考十分重要。「突然間很多科目 都要迫在一起溫習，一口氣要將兩年的課程塞進腦子裡，感到 有點壓力。」 Tommy 道。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n通宵讀書考試時睡著 <br />\n<br />\n考試前夕， Tommy 每晚通宵達旦溫習，有時更會捱至朝早六、七點。他回想起說：「這種讀書方法不太健康，捱通宵過後很疲累，考試時試題做到一半已經睡著了。」他建議會考同學應該提早溫習，考試前一晚只是重溫，臨急抱佛腳只會苦了自己。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n清早溫習最入腦 <br />\n<br />\nE-Kids 其餘兩位成員 Alan 和阿 Tim 一致認為清早讀書最有效。「臨 考前可以早兩小時起床，重溫前一晚溫習過的內容。那兩小 時你會很專心，既沒有電視機聲，也沒有其他人騷擾，我們 記歌詞都是用這個方法。」阿 Tim 說。 <br />\n<br />\n而 Tommy 則建議一班朋友到自修室溫習，一方面可以同朋友討 論課題，另一方面互相警惕對方，知道其他人勤力溫習，自 己不可以落後。他說溫習完畢大家一起食飯，談天說地，乘 機減壓。不過， Tommy 說要學會自制，不要自顧著與朋友玩 樂而忘記讀書，否則弄巧反掘。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/640pix/20030717/Article_ent/17ec4p4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2F640pix%2F20030717%2FArticle_ent%2F17ec4p4.jpg&h=041d0a1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aef55383e18651456a07da57fc8ee412d106922a","tid":317456,"uid":51933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:44:16.000Z","msg":"回一百次帶都係咁好笑"},{"pid":"4a37a9099f0d2775084f2e8da1b2a559c7e4f09f","tid":317456,"uid":1713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:44:51.000Z","msg":"三個加埋5分"},{"pid":"bc22682966050aa102c64961dd800f33215b15a7","tid":317456,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"張圖最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d6cbc6c25c593bc55a011dc5ae6b7596d2dfd6","tid":317456,"uid":38407,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:46:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三個加埋5分</blockquote><br />\nE-kids，加起來共1分 <br />\n<br />\n多年來均盛傳「三人相加不多於5分」，阮民安於2015年接受訪問時稱三人僅他一人應考，在數學科獲1分（即E級）"},{"pid":"191ff342b614af7db7b4e1e54e369c1f289c94c8","tid":317456,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T12:58:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba818ea434b3304d2c20c249ba95223191b2a2e0","tid":317456,"uid":121130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:10:07.000Z","msg":"三個加埋得一分 <br />\n叻仔"},{"pid":"3219830faeee664dd173d11285c5fb45cb1c35bd","tid":317456,"uid":38407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T15:16:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8334de3b85d6df4b42044045b9b84c0821b1b093","tid":317456,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e5f659248c441c854a1304afa9ed0a6bfc436c5","tid":317456,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T18:03:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇人認得Tommy以外嗰兩個個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我認得，但我最愛Tommy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce37819a5e380ea11e25ac26744fc68d739b0013","tid":317456,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T00:56:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe07729da202974b72d43e6649ada49389626b01","tid":317456,"uid":125310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:04:29.000Z","msg":"笑撚到抽筋"},{"pid":"1e3f111d27d54f335279d78d902df9fcc29b9e95","tid":317456,"uid":21716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T01:25:37.000Z","msg":"太監教人扑野"},{"pid":"3c27ff5820ed84b39a1cc255ae20eed2a82802a9","tid":317456,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r